<DIV3 TYPE="recipe">
<HEAD>Another.</HEAD>
<P>Take Costmary, drink it every day fastin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> wash thy teeth every night when thou go<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> to bed with Vinegar.</P>
