<DIV3 TYPE="recipe">
<HEAD>Against the Cough.</HEAD>
<P>Take Anniseeds Licquerice of each an ounce<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> Hysop one handful, sugar candy, four ounces, strong beer three pints, boil altogether till half be consu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ed, then strain forth the simples and give the patient every night, when he go|eth to bed four ounces warm.</P>
