<P>Take a Toste of bakers bread and pour <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> let oil on it, upon either side as you wo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> butter a toste, &amp; strew heaten Sugar on eit<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> side and use it first and last till you find ea<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"></P>
