<P>Take the root of Elicampane, Horehound, Hollihock of each alike much, seethe the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> altogether in white wine, with a dozen of sat Figgs and a little Liqu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">rice, drink of it a draught every day twice.</P>
