<DIV3 TYPE="recipe">
<HEAD>A Medicine for hoarsness in the throat.</HEAD>
<P>Take three or four figgs and cleave them in two every one, and then put into them <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> prettie quantity of Ginger finely beaten into powder, and then roste them upon a clean hearth or tile stone, and then let the partie eat them as hot as possible he can; This har<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> holpen some that have been troubled with hoarsness four or five years together before.</P>
