<P>Take Mal<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">owes and boil them with sheeps <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">llow till they be very tender, then strain it <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">d keep it in boxes and, if the brest have <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">eed to be tented, take a piece of the stalk of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">e Mallowes that are <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">dden, and tent it with|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">l, this is proved.</P>
