<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ith boars grease, and if you will, you may <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">dd sheepes suet, apply it hot, <HI>Probatum est.</HI></P>
