</DIV3>
<DIV3 TYPE="recipe">
<HEAD><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">or ach at the heart which are commonly a knot of worms.</HEAD>
<P>Take unset leeks one handful chopped small <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">d frie it with butter and bay salt, and lay it <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> the stomack upon a napkin.</P>
<P>Take a pinte of white wine, English liquerice <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> sugar, boil it together in a pot close stop|ed take it fasting<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></P>
