<P>Take of the confection of Alchermes two drams, of garden blew violet water and ex|cellent red rose water of each two ounces, and Syrup of violets two ounces and an half, and Syrup of Lymons one ounce&punc; mingle them well together and take hereof four or five spoon|fuls at a time when you see eause or when you please.</P>
