<PB N="89" REF="52">
to the party, and then cause him to take it e|very morning fasting, and about the clock <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n the afternoon. This drink is good against the scurvy, whosoever takes this drink spring and fall&punc; needs no other Medicine.</P>
