<P>The vertues are th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">se, it breaketh and di<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|solve <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n the st<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ne in the kidneys, causeth th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> patient to pisse, which otherwise is letted <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> a piece of flesh, it helpeth consumption, sci<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|tica, or ach in the head, fowl scurse, wounds i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> the head, It helpeth the plurifie. Give on
<PB N="189" REF="102">
dram with water at a time helpeth any swel|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ng in any part of the body, the coldness in <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">e head, it helpeth hot sickness aswell as cold.</P>
