<P>Take the Cucurbite with the saecis from whence this liquor was distilled and lute the said still over, then set it upon Ashes and make a hot fire and draw from it such liquor as will distill, And receive the said liquor into a bladder, which set under the nose o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> the Ale<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|bick and keep it and therewith anoint the skin or outward parts, and they shall be preser|ved from the Contagion, as aforesaid.</P>
